    "<b><u>Please see the Cybersecurity MS Handbook or talk to an academic advisor for a complete list of approved Cybersecurity Graduate Electives</u></b>",
    "<b>* CS/CSEC BS/MS Double-Counted Courses</b> (however see ** also)",
    "<b>** If approved CSEC Grad. Adv. Elec. that are Comp. Sci. (CSCI) courses are selected as double-counts, the BS double-count can satisfy CS Elective requirements instead of Open Electives<b>",
